Kelvin Andre SPOTTS, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-9491. Supreme Court of the United States April 28, 2014. Case below, 537 Fed.Appx. 208 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
